{
  "text": "Methodological quality assessment was accomplished using the Downs and Black checklist. The total cumulative score is composed of a profile that measures quality of reporting, internal validity, and external validity. According to Downs and Black, the performance results of the checklist showed a high internal consistency (Kuder-Richardson formula 20 \u00bc 0.89) and test-retest (r \u00bc 0.88) and interrater (r \u00bc 0.75) reliability. [CITATION_1] The checklist consists of 27 items for which a \"yes\" answer is scored 1 and \"no\" or \"unable to determine\" answer is scored 0. ",
